@0=~(The Narzugon has fled to another part of Avernus. You feel that the barrier surrounding the tower has weakened; you resolve to free Caelar and get out of here before the baatezu can return with reinforcements.)~
@1=~Impressive. But this is not the end, <CHARNAME>. I'll find a way back to the Prime Material Plane, and when I do...~
@2=~(The tower shakes and shudders violently as the dampening field weakens.)~
@3=~We need to get out of here, NOW!~
@4=~The tower's about to collapse! Grab Caelar and get us out of here!~
@5=~Now would definitely be a good time to leave!~
@6=~We're out of time!~
@7=~What are you waiting for! Get Caelar and teleport us out of here!~